CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: U Power Ltd is involved in the provision of vehicle sourcing services. It is principally engaged in the provision of new energy vehicles development and sales; battery swapping stations manufactory and sales; battery swapping services and sourcing services. The company as a broker engaged in sales of vehicles between automobile wholesalers and buyers, including small and medium sized vehicle dealers and individual customers primarily located in the lower-tier cities in China, which are smaller and less developed than the tier-1 or tier-2 cities.
